## Zoy

Utility to count lines of python code, scripts, directories, etc. in projects.

```bash
$ python -m zoy path/to/project
Project Structure: 
ðŸ“‚ test
  ðŸ“„ test_zoy.py
ðŸ“‚ zoy
  ðŸ“„ zoy.py
  ðŸ“„ __init__.py
  ðŸ“„ __main__.py

=========================================

Total Python files: 4
Total lines in Python files: 65
Total directories: 2
```

### Installation

```bash
$ pip install zoy
```
